{"tid":2410903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昨日，我菲律賓工人行過街市，聽到有個賣魚佬講話有條友仔叫黃世澤，將我放咗喺個咩5毛黨名冊","createTime":"2021-02-17T03:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T07:46:12.000Z","uid":150100,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f1b813f4630005234c5aed74158c5a699129e435","tid":2410903,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:34:43.000Z","msg":"哈哈&hellip;&hellip;我當堂嚇一跳，然後得啖笑。"},{"pid":"e5c79ed357cdd2ff751857da212aea2b5d647390","tid":2410903,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"我就叫不Gay的瘋，你屙尿都要除褲，我就睬你都㩄氣，直接屙落條褲嘅，呢啲就叫特異功能"},{"pid":"e9d992e14f904c8806265cf024085d8897afb1ca","tid":2410903,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:39:59.000Z","msg":"你話我講嘢無厘頭，我夠話你未瞓醒戇九九咯。望咩呀？條氣唔順呀？ 出嚟隻揪呀。當然，你要補番一百幾廿萬過我就唔在講㗎啦。睥咩呀？學嘢唔使錢呀？抄低我聯絡電話係︰（香港）99945678，我再重覆一次係︰（香港）99945678。你唔搵我我無所謂，因為呢啲係你嘅損失。十點鐘後唔好打嚟，因為我瞓咗！"},{"pid":"7f89054e601f5fc78b9efc1cb2961104c76aec13","tid":2410903,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"有名你叫 律師信魔人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08f09af37fb020f3384298b7efcd984688b9209","tid":2410903,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7f89054e601f5fc78b9efc1cb2961104c76aec13","tid":2410903,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"有名你叫 律師信魔人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:58:50.000Z","msg":"我真係識佢老鼠"},{"pid":"8e44831c64af6ee4a6a2654e3abd6bd313dd7085","tid":2410903,"uid":19557,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:07:10.000Z","msg":"但你真係五毛喎..."},{"pid":"138e12e2d867080f509bee325ed7b4ffa7a97b13","tid":2410903,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e44831c64af6ee4a6a2654e3abd6bd313dd7085","tid":2410903,"uid":19557,"